event: STREAM_CHUNK
data: {"message_id":"41151322251708418","patch_op":[{"patch_object":1,"patch_type":1,"patch_value":{"content_block":[{"block_type":10025,"block_id":"9382801558394114","parent_id":"9382801558176770","content":{"search_query_result_block":{"summary":"搜索 4 个关键词，参考 27 篇资料","queries":["2026美加墨世界杯 热度实力TOP10球队 最新排名","2026 FIFA World Cup top 10 teams by strength and popularity predictions","2026世界杯 夺冠热门 实力排名 最新","2026世界杯 已晋级球队 实力分析 热门程度"],"results":[{"text_card":{"id":9382801558500354,"summary":"<tr><th>#FC</th><th>SELECCIÓN</th><th>VOTOS COMO #1</th><th>RANKING FIFA</th><th>ÚLTIMO MUNDIAL</th></tr>\n<tr><td>1.</td><td>España</td><td>15</td><td>1</td><td>Octavos de final</td></tr>\n<tr><td>2.</td><...\n","title":"ESPN FC: Power Rankings a 100 días del Mundial 2026","sitename":"ESPN Deportes","url":"https://espndeportes.espn.com/futbol/mundial/nota/_/id/16379952/mundial-2026-100-dias-ranking-selecciones-candidatas-espn-fc","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/fab56abd026a1ea49754538e6f68b758~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=Gz5ifvXikaYxi9Yg%2FvfnPdYyyCg%3D","doc_id":"fce56f69ca8e1f3f-293a96b7aceaa227","publish_time_second":"2026-03-03T07:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":1,"index":1}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558500610,"summary":"世界排名第四的英格兰队以15.4%紧随其后。现世界排名第二的阿根廷队，世界排名第三的法国队以及世界排名第五的巴西队均以11.1%的概率并列第3。世界排名第六的葡萄牙...\n现世界排名第32的挪威队，在魔王哈兰德和厄德高双子星的率领下，时隔28年重返世界杯正赛舞台，目前以3.8%的概率排名第9。","title":"美加 墨 世界杯 最新 夺冠 概率 新鲜 出炉 评论 留下 你 心目 中 的 冠军 队伍 吧 # 世界杯 # 美加 墨 世界杯 # 世界杯 竞猜 # 世界杯 冠军","sitename":"抖音","url":"https://www.iesdouyin.com/share/video/7619248668713609657","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/27422dd3ce8d2f41b45309e5aeca806b~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=9b6u3OwSNw6M9DOaFZABaL2dMdo%3D","doc_id":"7619248668713609657","publish_time_second":"2026-03-20T16:16:12+08:00","original_doc_rank":3,"index":2}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558500866,"summary":"根据《体育画报》发布的世界杯参赛国实力排名，前五名依次为西班牙、阿根廷、英格兰、法国和葡萄牙，日本队位列第17位。该杂志特别提到：“最引人注目的是森保一执教的日本队，此次排名中日本位列第17位。”\n报道指出，日本...\n本月初，美国体育专业媒体ESPN发布的实力排名中，日本队同样位列第15位，而韩国队无缘榜单。","title":"美媒发布2026年男足世界杯“实力排名”，亚洲仅日本国家队上榜 韩国队遗憾落榜_中华网","sitename":"中华网","url":"https://3g.china.com/act/news/10000169/20260325/49355892.html","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/de983b4feb89444f2e3c0b2fd1be8a6b~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=gDLhnj2kkxcu7067vJkVWSB6qp8%3D","doc_id":"34ab71c5199b33b5-7ee73ed0691f761f","publish_time_second":"2026-03-25T19:16:29+08:00","original_doc_rank":4,"index":3}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558501122,"summary":"ESPN15强排名（队伍/目前国际足联排名）\n1.西班牙 1\n2.法国 3\n3.阿根廷 2\n4.英格兰 4\n5.巴西 5\n6.葡萄牙 6\n7.德国 10\n8.荷兰 7\n9.摩洛哥 8\n10.哥伦比亚 14\n11.比利时 9\n12.挪威 32\n13.塞内加尔 ...\n","title":"360体育-ESPN评世界杯15强战力榜:西法前两名，阿根廷第三葡萄牙第六","sitename":"PP体育","url":"https://www.ppsports.com/360news/news/2496749.html","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/b5817172c53226088db591ffb4822443~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=dsfwJJA%2BP8LvxOgoRux2rX41eMs%3D","doc_id":"c3d46c5008fec62d-0d60a33f628424e5","publish_time_second":"2026-03-05T23:24:41+08:00","original_doc_rank":5,"index":4}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558501378,"summary":"以下...\n20.乌拉圭\n19.科特迪瓦\n18.瑞士\n17.日本\n16.比利时\n15.厄瓜多尔\n14.美国队\n13.哥伦比亚\n12.克罗地亚\n11.塞内加尔\n10.巴西\n9.德国\n8.摩洛哥\n7.荷兰\n6.挪威\n5.葡萄牙\n4.法国\n3.英格兰\n2.阿根廷\n1.西班牙\n","title":"2026世界杯实力榜:西班牙、阿根廷领跑，挪威成最大黑马_茜茜爱体育","sitename":"今日头条","url":"http://m.toutiao.com/group/7619425652436894260/","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/118f7a3625ad8ebbbc11d04f118d2e10~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=YGdvNZvNExIVOqU4lW5bhbe90Ag%3D","doc_id":"686aef676ec583ba-5c5af44fb3496737","publish_time_second":"2026-03-21T03:43:49+08:00","original_doc_rank":6,"index":5}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558501634,"summary":"第一名：西班牙\n在本次首次实力榜评选中，西班牙获得21张第一名选票中的15张，几乎一边倒地占据榜首。\n在预选赛中，他们以6战5胜的成绩力压保加利亚、土耳其和格鲁吉亚晋级，虽然表现谈不上惊艳，但进攻端拥有亚马尔 、佩...\n第二名：法国\n第三名：阿根廷\n第四名：英格兰\n第五名：巴西\n第六名：葡萄牙\n第七名：德国\n第八名：荷兰\n","title":"世界杯倒计时100天!ESPN最新实力榜出炉:西班牙居首，巴西仅第五!_腾讯新闻","sitename":"腾讯网","url":"http://news.qq.com/rain/a/20260304A0602300","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/4de782aa583bda88c8448344ff36c656~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=7XEob2fHAIPvJ7yvG%2FJQkac396Y%3D","doc_id":"6219fad32ccff4d8-6a8d6fbafb1087c6","publish_time_second":"2026-03-04T18:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":7,"index":6}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558501890,"summary":"2) Argentina – 1873.33 points\nThe reigning World Champions, Argentina will be looking to retain their crown this summer, and are only really behind Spain as the favourites. They’re certainly looking as strong as ever as they sit fourth in the world...\n10) Germany – 1724.15 points\nGermany haven’t been at their best for some time, despite a great history in World Cups, of which they’ve won four. ","title":"FIFA World rankings: How the top 10 national teams rank ahead of 2026 World Cup","sitename":"OneFootball","url":"https://onefootball.com/es/noticias/fifa-world-rankings-how-the-top-10-national-teams-rank-ahead-of-2026-world-cup-42577227","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/a642257d6790afa64c4c328e19d53907~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=Ys82gFsr7OzY2KYZQup014pn3i4%3D","doc_id":"1fc066f26afec3b8-f44d7cfbb7849acc","publish_time_second":"2026-03-18T00:00:00+08:00","index":7}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558502146,"summary":"England follows closely at +550 to +6...\nBrazil and defending champion Argentina round out the top tier at +750 to +800, with Brazil's attacking flair and Argentina's Lionel Messi-led experience (potentially his final tournament) making them perennial threats.\nPortugal (+1100), Germany (+1200 to +1400) and the Netherlands (+1600 to +2000) follow as strong challengers. ","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup Predictions: Spain Emerges as Clear Favorite with Expanded 48-Team Format Looming","sitename":"International Business Times AU","url":"https://www.ibtimes.com.au/2026-fifa-world-cup-predictions-spain-emerges-clear-favorite-expanded-48-team-format-looming-1863768","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/e618e4983e3b1d58d9f9cb17e50edc15~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=qQQ4nqagZ5ZSU7%2BbGkrO1CSzJyw%3D","doc_id":"6e8c56ea17907dea-baa776922ff2a2d7","publish_time_second":"2026-03-19T13:29:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":2,"index":8}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558502402,"summary":"FIFA men’s world ranking points: 1834.12\n5. Brazil National Soccer TeamBrazil climbs into top 5 under new manager Carlo Ancelotti. The Seleção currently sits fifth in the CONMEBOL World Cup qualifying standings and continues its quest to return to World Cup glory.\nThe team features a mix of established stars and exciting young talents as they build toward the 2026 tournament.\nBrazil’s Current Squad:\nGoalkeepers: Al...\n","title":"FIFA Men’s Power Ranking","sitename":"FIFA World Cup News","url":"https://www.fifaworldcupnews.com/fifa-mens-world-ranking/","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/69b675c19f3c02e55ee2ddefd0d903e7~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=5MoNsGEpY1E8QD%2FZSZo8uBr9Q3U%3D","doc_id":"9e5d51b52390b8e8-b572c1b2dbe3fe72","publish_time_second":"2026-03-05T00:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":3,"index":9}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558502914,"summary":"Can Spain Win the World Cup 2026?\nVerdict: 65-70% likelihood of reaching the semi-finals; 35-40% likelihood of winning the tournament.\nThe Case Against Spain\nInjury uncertainties surrounding Yamal, Rodri, Pedri, and Williams create significant depth concerns in a short tournament where recovery time is nonexistent. The groin injury plaguing Yamal (involving pain with cutting and turning—...\n","title":"Spain World Cup 2026 Analysis – Can Spain Win?","sitename":"FIFA World Cup News","url":"https://www.fifaworldcupnews.com/spain-world-cup-26-analysis-can-spain-win/","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/69b675c19f3c02e55ee2ddefd0d903e7~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=5MoNsGEpY1E8QD%2FZSZo8uBr9Q3U%3D","doc_id":"9423e02651a1de0b-4814deffacaa7ccd","publish_time_second":"2025-12-22T00:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":4,"index":10}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558503170,"summary":"FIFA World Cup 2026 Outright Betting Odds: Favourites, Predictions and Team-by-Team Analysis of the Top Options\nCheck out the current latest betting odds for the 2026 FIFA World Cup Outright winner market.\nby Ian John\non March 23rd, 2026\nThe countdown to the 2026 FIFA World Cup Finals is gathering pace, and with qualification nearing completion, attention is turning sharply towards the...\n","title":"FIFA World Cup 2026 Outright Betting Odds: Favourites, Predictions and Team-by-Team Analysis of the Top Options","sitename":"BonusCodePoker","url":"https://bonuscodepoker.com/fifa-world-cup-2026-outright-betting-odds","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/bf7868ee62b51bafbcd125e90540deba~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=%2FPGP98kFOUsl8PHGxwl5GlplBgs%3D","doc_id":"2ac3c8d314560bed-cada97dfb18e1603","publish_time_second":"2026-03-23T00:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":5,"index":11}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558503426,"summary":"Argentina is in a golden era that delivered the 2021 Copa América, the 2022 Finalissima, and the 2022 World Cup.\nNow, they aren’t just Lionel...\nThe appointment of Thomas Tuchel has introduced a pragmatic, tournament-winning DNA that many felt was missing during the Gareth Southgate era.\nEngland currently boasts the highest Squad Market Value in the tournament, with Jude Bellingham and Phil Foden reaching their peaks simultaneously.\n","title":"2026 FIFA World Cup Predictions: Top 5 Strongest Contenders","sitename":"TWSN Sports","url":"https://twsn.net/2026/03/05/2026-fifa-world-cup-predictions-5-contenders/","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/402146bf5a99b0739e2883ea3f04750b~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbnail.jpeg?rk3s=feb11e32&x-expires=1779702515&x-signature=u%2BivekDsQS5hd6NZD0Y%2BKdJX6W0%3D","doc_id":"7bc275e28e0a70fd-7f03e76ca1dfa73b","publish_time_second":"2026-03-05T00:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":6,"index":12}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558503682,"summary":"charnsitr / Shutterstock.com\nWith odds also at 66/1, Japan brings organization, technique, and tactical sharpness to every tournament. They’ve steadily climbed the global ranks and have the...\nRingo Chiu / Shutterstock.com\nAlways passionate and unpredictable, Mexico is listed at 50/1 and could benefit from the home advantage. Their tournament experience and massive local support might give them just enough fire to reach the latter stages.\n15. Denmark","title":"Top 20 Favorites to Win the 2026 FIFA World Cup","sitename":"Lentedesportiva","url":"https://lentedesportiva.com/top-20-favorites-to-win-the-2026-fifa-world-cup/","doc_id":"1194cfd25ebdb8c8-116ba920729500f8","publish_time_second":"2025-12-29T00:00:00+08:00","original_doc_rank":7,"index":13}},{"text_card":{"id":9382801558504450,"summary":"就在距离世界杯开幕不足百天之际，权威数据机构OPTA发布了最新的夺冠概率预测，为我们勾勒出一幅充满看点与悬念的争冠图景。\n根据OPTA超级计算机基于球队表现、历史数据和市场动态进行的上万次模拟，西班牙以17%的概率高居榜首，法国(14.1%)和英格兰(11.8%)分列二三位，卫冕冠军阿根廷以8.7%排名第四。然而，随着...\n","title":"OPTA最新预测美加墨世界杯冠军:西班牙居首，葡萄牙仅排第六_蜥蜴体育","sitename":"今日头条","url":"http://m.toutiao.com/group/7620603628331483658/","logo_url":"https://p3-spider-image-sign.byteimg.com/isp-i18n-media/img/118f7a3625ad8ebbbc11d04f118d2e10~tplv-e9ol9do63j-thumbna